<br>
FURTHERMORE, I'm not at all certain that the duty is to the group over the guild. If a raid is called, hopefully I have enough warning to let my group know I'm leaving soon. But if not - if it's a race to a named, &quot;Peace, yo - raid called&quot; and /disband. I'm *pretty sure* most people would say guild &gt; group, especially if it's a pickup group.<br>
<br>
Finally why *shouldn't* he tell his guild that there's a possilbe named. All-in-all I think DoN handled this situation with class, especially if they're helping make it easier for you to pull and not jumping your named.<br>
